Package: WRBdatabase
Title: Hydrological database creation and maintenance
Version: 1.0.0-0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ghislain", "de Laplante", , "ghislaindel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5093-9185"))
Description: Set of functions for the initial creation and ongoing
    maintenance of WRB's local database. This local database is a
    combination of the Water Survey of Canada real-time and historical
    data and WRB data held in Aquarius; in addition, multiple parameters
    are calculated to facilitate reporting and graphically representing
    data.
